{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"UIEvent.detail","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><em><code>detail</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/sourceCapabilities\"><code>sourceCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/view\"><code>view</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/which\"><code>which</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>UIEvent.detail</code></strong> 是只读属性, 当值为非空的时候，提供当前点击数 (和环境有关) 。</p>\n\n<p>对 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">click (en-US)</a></code> 或者&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/dblclick_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dblclick (en-US)</a></code> 事件，<code>UIEvent.detail</code>&nbsp;是当前点击数量。</p>\n\n<p>对 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mousedown_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">mousedown (en-US)</a></code> 或者&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mouseup_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">mouseup (en-US)</a></code> 事件，<code>UIEvent.detail</code> 是 1 加上当前点击数。</p>\n\n<p>对所有的其它<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a> 对象，<code>UIEvent.detail</code>&nbsp;总是零。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#dom-uievent-detail","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.UIEvent.detail"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.UIEvent.detail","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"UIEvent.detail 是只读属性, 当值为非空的时候，提供当前点击数 (和环境有关) 。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"UIEvent.detail","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"UIEvent.detail","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"UIEvent.detail","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/uievent/detail","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/uievent/detail/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent","title":"UIEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail","title":"UIEvent.detail"}],"pageTitle":"UIEvent.detail - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}